com.epoch.energyDiagrams

Class EDiagram

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.epoch.energyDiagrams.EDiagram
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    EDiagramConstants, EnergyQDatumConstants
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OED, RCD

    public class EDiagram
extends Object
implements EDiagramConstants
    A diagram in which the y-axis is energy. Consists of a table, each cell of which may contain one or more items.

      • getCompareLines

        public List<String> getCompareLines()
        Returns lines with empty rows removed (so rows are numbered 1, 2, ...) but with the rows kept in their order within each column. E.g., lines 13=1:3=2/5=1:15=2 will become 2=1:1=2/1=1:2=2.
        Returns:
        a list of strings representing lines that have been vertically compressed
